Package: UHHformats
Type: Package
Title: Templates for HTML and PDF/LaTeX Output Formats Designed for the UHH
Version: 0.1.1.9000
Date: 2022-7-16
Authors@R: c(person("Saskia", "Otto", email="saskia.a.otto@gmail.com",
    role=c("aut","cre")))
Maintainer: Saskia Otto <saskia.a.otto@gmail.com>
Description: R Markdown templates for HTML and PDF documents, which are used within the 
    Biology Department of the University of Hamburg (UHH) and its 'Data Science in Biology'
    program. These include templates for student assignments, project reports,
    and conversions to Jupyter Notebooks. The package aims to encourage
    reproducible research using simple Markdown syntax while embedding all of the R code to 
    produce plots and analyses as well. All templates are inspired by or based on other 
    packages such as 'rmdformats', 'ireports' or 'rmd2jupyter'.
